title: California Firm Recalls Ready-To-Eat Meals Produced Without Benefit of Inspection
summary: Editor's Note: This recall release is being reissued to expand the Oct. 26 recall to include additional products. WASHINGTON, Nov. 2, 2011 - Judy's Catering, LLC., a Burbank, Calif., establishment, is expanding its recall of ready-to-eat chicken, turkey, beef and pork products by an undetermined...
